cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.GT, cs.CV. 

The paper uses neuroevolution, a subfield of artificial intelligence, to evolve neural networks for controlling units in real-time strategy games. Therefore, cs.AI is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves machine learning techniques such as neural networks, which falls under cs.LG. The use of neuroevolution specifically falls under cs.NE. The paper also involves game theory, which is covered under cs.GT. Finally, the paper mentions the use of computer vision techniques for analyzing game states, which falls under cs.CV.
